          img src="/images/2011/konex.jpg" alt="Ciudad Cultural Konex"
        li
          img src="/images/2011/eto.jpg" alt="Koichiro Eto"
        li
          img src="/images/2011/rc2011.jpg" alt="RubyConf Argentina 2011"

